# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets reads this file to set response headers.
# The dashboard is a single app shell (index.html) that fetches live weather
# data at runtime, so the HTML/JS itself changes only on deploy. Without an
# explicit Cache-Control, browsers fall back to heuristic caching and can keep
# serving an old index.html after a deploy. "no-cache" lets the browser store
# the file but forces it to revalidate with the server (via ETag) on every
# load, so a new deploy shows up immediately while unchanged loads still return
# a cheap 304.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
